Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.00,OP-R,,0,0,0,,Yobidasareta watashi wa ja no kami (ja no kami)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.63,OP-R,,0,0,0,,Ano ko wo yanakya, makai e
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.50,OP-R,,0,0,0,,Kaeremasen no! (Onee-chan...)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:56.22,OP-R,,0,0,0,,Tsune ni shi to tonariawase chein sou ousen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:58.14,OP-R,,0,0,0,,Fuzake ga sugitanaraba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:02.14,OP-R,,0,0,0,,gittagitta ni kirikizande yare!
