Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.61,OP-R,,0,0,0,,Yudan shita na Yurine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:22.78,OP-R,,0,0,0,,Ima da! Dai ni no satsujingi Royal Copenhagen!
